text: Muldakayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 253 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 74 km from Uchaly, 1 km from Ilchigulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Muldakayevo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
